node.text:
DUNKED - @coco.atelier has completely transformed this Tel Aviv apartment into a plush modern open living space perfect for a bachelor/ bachelorette!
 
The materials, details, fixtures and fittings have been elected to play a role individually but also collectively. Stone is scattered throughout the space, bespoke painted wall panelling wraps around the bed offering a welcome visual contrast, whilst the floor transitions from tile to timber to subtly break up this open masterpiece.

The shower is a head turner, not least because of it’s open nature but also the grand spectacle that this full height focal piece creates across the whole floor!

Let us know your thoughts in the comments!

PHOTOGRAPHY - @odedsmadar
